ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
SubjectMemorandum of Undersdanting with provinces and territories re: National Air Pollution Surveillance Program
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of the Environment to sign a Memorandum of Understanding with the Provinces and Territories in order to formalize arrangements pertaining to the management of the federal/provincial-territorial NATIONAL AIR POLLUTANT SURVEILLANCE PROGRAM.
